import React from 'react'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
const BasicInfo = () => {
  return (
     <Card className='mb-3 '>
       <Card.Header>
        Basic Info
       </Card.Header>
       <Card.Body>
       <Form.Group className="mb-3">
       <Form.Label>Disabled input</Form.Label>
       <Form.Control placeholder="Disabled input"  />
     </Form.Group>
       
     </Card.Body>
     </Card>
  )
}

export default BasicInfo
